1
00:00:02,377 --> 00:00:05,046
[EXOTIC MUSIC PLAYING]

2
00:00:51,092 --> 00:00:53,637
CAPTAIN, I THINK I'M
GOING TO LIKE ARGELIUS.

3
00:00:53,679 --> 00:00:56,097
OBVIOUSLY A MAN
OF GOOD TASTE.

4
00:00:56,139 --> 00:00:58,141
YOU MEAN TO TELL ME
THAT ALL THESE WOMEN--

5
00:00:58,183 --> 00:00:59,351
WELL, THAT ALL THIS IS--

6
00:00:59,393 --> 00:01:01,478
YES, YES, YES.
MM-HMM.

7
00:01:01,520 --> 00:01:04,565
THE ARGELIANS
THINK VERY HIGHLY
OF THEIR PLEASURE.

8
00:01:04,606 --> 00:01:06,859
WELL, NOW, THAT'S
AN UNDERSTATEMENT
IF I EVER HEARD ONE.

9
00:01:06,901 --> 00:01:09,611
THIS IS A COMPLETELY
HEDONISTIC SOCIETY.

10
00:01:22,123 --> 00:01:23,500
YOU LIKE HER, SCOTTY?

11
00:01:23,542 --> 00:01:25,168
AYE.

12
00:01:25,210 --> 00:01:26,628
WHY SHOULDN'T I?

13
00:01:26,670 --> 00:01:29,130
GOOD. I'VE INVITED
HER TO JOIN US
AT THE TABLE.

14
00:01:29,172 --> 00:01:30,925
I THOUGHT YOU MIGHT
LIKE TO MEET HER.

15
00:01:30,966 --> 00:01:33,928
NOW, THAT'S WHAT I CALL
A REAL CAPTAIN--

16
00:01:33,969 --> 00:01:35,429
ALWAYS THINKING
OF HIS MEN.

17
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:26,229
[BANGING]

18
00:02:26,271 --> 00:02:29,817
SCOTTY,
SCOTTY, IN ARGELIUS
THEY USE THE LIGHTS.

19
00:02:29,858 --> 00:02:32,111
NOW, NO ONE HAS TO TELL
AN OLD ABERDEEN PUB-CRAWLER

20
00:02:32,152 --> 00:02:33,821
HOW TO APPLAUD, CAPTAIN.

21
00:02:40,285 --> 00:02:42,496
Kirk:
HAVE ONE OF OUR PILLOWS?

22
00:02:49,168 --> 00:02:52,171
'TIS A FINE FOGGY NIGHT
TONIGHT, AND I DOUBT

23
00:02:52,213 --> 00:02:54,341
IF ANYONE HAS EVER TOLD
YOU OF THE MARVELOUS

24
00:02:54,382 --> 00:02:55,676
FOGS WE HAVE
IN ABERDEEN.

25
00:02:55,717 --> 00:02:57,511
Woman: NEVER A WORD,

26
00:02:57,552 --> 00:02:59,513
BUT I'M DYING
TO LEARN.

27
00:02:59,554 --> 00:03:01,473
WELL, THEN, WHY
DON'T I SHOW YOU?

28
00:03:01,515 --> 00:03:04,601
THERE'S NOTHING LIKE
A WALK IN THE FOG
WITH A BONNY LASS.

29
00:03:04,643 --> 00:03:07,938
OR A...HANDSOME GENTLEMAN.

30
00:03:07,980 --> 00:03:09,481
Woman: WHY DON'T WE?

31
00:03:12,359 --> 00:03:13,944
YOU DON'T MIND,
DO YOU?

32
00:03:13,986 --> 00:03:15,904
I MIGHT EVEN GET
BACK TO THE SHIP
ON TIME.

33
00:03:15,946 --> 00:03:17,114
WE WON'T LEAVE
WITHOUT YOU,
SCOTTY.

34
00:03:17,156 --> 00:03:18,866
RELAX AND ENJOY
YOURSELF.

35
00:03:21,242 --> 00:03:23,912
MY WORK
IS NEVER DONE.

36
00:03:23,954 --> 00:03:27,332
McCoy: MY WORK, JIM.
THIS IS PRESCRIPTION STUFF.

37
00:03:27,374 --> 00:03:29,417
DON'T FORGET,
THE EXPLOSION
THAT THREW SCOTTY

38
00:03:29,459 --> 00:03:32,004
AGAINST A BULKHEAD WAS
CAUSED BY A WOMAN.

39
00:03:32,046 --> 00:03:33,463
PHYSICALLY
HE'S ALL RIGHT.

40
00:03:33,505 --> 00:03:35,298
AM I RIGHT
IN ASSUMING THAT?

41
00:03:35,340 --> 00:03:37,467
OH, YES, YES
AND, MATTER OF FACT,

42
00:03:37,509 --> 00:03:40,512
CONSIDERABLE
PSYCHOLOGICAL DAMAGE
COULD HAVE BEEN CAUSED--

43
00:03:40,554 --> 00:03:43,264
FOR EXAMPLE, HIS TOTAL
RESENTMENT TOWARD WOMEN.

44
00:03:43,306 --> 00:03:45,308
HE SEEMS
TO BE OVERCOMING
HIS RESENTMENT.

45
00:03:45,350 --> 00:03:47,936
OF COURSE, IN MY
PROFESSIONAL OPINION, WHEN
HE GETS BACK TO THE SHIP,

46
00:03:47,978 --> 00:03:50,689
HE'S GOING TO HATE YOU FOR
MAKING HIM LEAVE ARGELIUS,

47
00:03:50,731 --> 00:03:54,026
BUT THEN, HE WILL HAVE
LOST TOTAL RESENTMENT
TOWARD WOMEN.

48
00:03:54,068 --> 00:03:58,072
MISSION ACCOMPLISHED
AS FAR AS SCOTTY
IS CONCERNED.

49
00:03:58,113 --> 00:03:59,698
BONES...
HMM?

50
00:03:59,740 --> 00:04:01,700
I KNOW
A LITTLE PLACE

51
00:04:01,742 --> 00:04:03,284
ACROSS TOWN
WHERE THE WOMEN--

52
00:04:03,326 --> 00:04:04,369
OH, YES, I KNOW THE PLACE.

53
00:04:04,411 --> 00:04:06,329
I KNOW THE PLACE.
LET'S GO.

54
00:04:32,814 --> 00:04:34,482
I THINK IT'S THAT WAY.

55
00:04:34,524 --> 00:04:36,568
I THINK IT'S
THAT WAY, TOO.

56
00:04:36,610 --> 00:04:38,653
[WOMAN SCREAMS]

57
00:04:50,290 --> 00:04:52,542
SHE'S DEAD, JIM.

58
00:04:52,584 --> 00:04:54,962
STABBED A DOZEN TIMES.

59
00:04:55,003 --> 00:04:57,047
[MOANING]

60
00:05:15,190 --> 00:05:18,902
Kirk: SPACE--
THE FINAL FRONTIER.

61
00:05:24,158 --> 00:05:28,203
THESE ARE THE VOYAGES
OF THE STARSHIP "ENTERPRISE."

62
00:05:28,245 --> 00:05:30,164
ITS FIVE-YEAR MISSION--

63
00:05:30,205 --> 00:05:32,791
TO EXPLORE
STRANGE, NEW WORLDS...

64
00:05:32,833 --> 00:05:36,795
TO SEEK OUT NEW LIFE
AND NEW CIVILIZATIONS...

65
00:05:36,837 --> 00:05:39,965
TO BOLDLY GO WHERE
NO MAN HAS GONE BEFORE.

66
00:06:23,175 --> 00:06:24,676
Kirk: "CAPTAIN'S LOG,

67
00:06:24,718 --> 00:06:26,303
"STARDATE 3614.9.

68
00:06:26,345 --> 00:06:28,263
"PLANET ARGELIUS II.

69
00:06:28,305 --> 00:06:30,473
"WHILE ON THERAPEUTIC
SHORE LEAVE,

70
00:06:30,515 --> 00:06:32,684
"MR. SCOTT HAS
FALLEN UNDER SUSPICION

71
00:06:32,726 --> 00:06:35,687
"OF HAVING BRUTALLY MURDERED
AN ARGELIAN WOMAN.

72
00:06:35,729 --> 00:06:39,066
"THE CHIEF CITY ADMINISTRATOR,
A MR. HENGIST,

73
00:06:39,107 --> 00:06:41,318
"HAS TAKEN CHARGE
OF THE INVESTIGATION,

74
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:42,736
BUT HAS LEARNED
LITTLE OF VALUE."

75
00:06:42,777 --> 00:06:44,946
Hengist: I DON'T KNOW
WHAT TO SAY, GENTLEMEN.

76
00:06:44,988 --> 00:06:48,449
ARGELIUS IS THE LAST PLANET
IN THE GALAXY I'D EXPECT
A THING LIKE THIS TO HAPPEN.

77
00:06:48,491 --> 00:06:51,161
WE'RE JUST
AS SHOCKED AS YOU
ARE, MR. HENGIST.

78
00:06:51,203 --> 00:06:53,080
IF THIS WAS
MY HOME PLANET, RIGEL IV,

79
00:06:53,121 --> 00:06:55,123
I'D HAVE A DOZEN
INVESTIGATORS WORKING
ON THE MATTER,

80
00:06:55,165 --> 00:06:57,209
BUT THEY DON'T
EXIST HERE.

81
00:06:57,251 --> 00:07:00,003
YOU'RE NOT A NATIVE
OF ARGELIUS, SIR?

82
00:07:00,045 --> 00:07:03,048
OH, NO, NO. ARGELIUS HIRES
ITS ADMINISTRATIVE OFFICERS

83
00:07:03,090 --> 00:07:04,966
FROM OTHER PLANETS. HEH!

84
00:07:05,008 --> 00:07:07,052
THE ARGELIANS AREN'T
VERY EFFICIENT, YOU KNOW,

85
00:07:07,094 --> 00:07:10,013
A GENTLE, HARMLESS PEOPLE.

86
00:07:10,055 --> 00:07:13,683
UH, MR. SCOTT.
UH, MR. SCOTT.

87
00:07:13,725 --> 00:07:15,227
NOW, UH, ARE YOU SURE

88
00:07:15,269 --> 00:07:16,853
YOU'VE NEVER
SEEN THIS BEFORE?

89
00:07:16,895 --> 00:07:20,065
I--I DON'T REMEMBER.

90
00:07:20,107 --> 00:07:22,192
Hengist: REALLY, SIR,
THAT IS HARDLY HELPFUL.

91
00:07:22,234 --> 00:07:24,903
SCOTTY...

92
00:07:24,945 --> 00:07:26,780
YOU LEFT THE CAFE
WITH THE GIRL.

93
00:07:26,821 --> 00:07:28,407
DO YOU
REMEMBER THAT?

94
00:07:28,448 --> 00:07:30,075
WHAT
HAPPENED NEXT?

95
00:07:30,117 --> 00:07:31,701
[SIGHS]

96
00:07:31,743 --> 00:07:33,954
WELL, WE WERE...

97
00:07:33,995 --> 00:07:37,749
WALKING IN...THE FOG.

98
00:07:37,791 --> 00:07:41,169
UH, I WAS UP AHEAD

99
00:07:41,211 --> 00:07:43,630
TRYING TO LEAD THE WAY.

100
00:07:43,671 --> 00:07:45,715
I HEARD THE GIRL SCREAM.

101
00:07:47,550 --> 00:07:50,178
I REMEMBER
STARTING TO TURN.

102
00:07:50,220 --> 00:07:53,432
I DON'T REMEMBER
ANOTHER THING.

103
00:07:53,473 --> 00:07:54,891
SCOTTY,
YOU'VE GOT
TO REMEMBER.

104
00:07:54,933 --> 00:07:56,601
JIM.

105
00:08:00,230 --> 00:08:02,441
IF HE SAYS
HE CAN'T REMEMBER,
HE PROBABLY DOESN'T.

106
00:08:02,482 --> 00:08:03,942
YOU KNOW SCOTTY.

107
00:08:03,984 --> 00:08:06,278
I KNOW THAT A MURDER
HAS BEEN COMMITTED.

108
00:08:06,320 --> 00:08:08,113
YOU DON'T THINK,
BY ANY CHANCE,
THAT SCOTTY WAS--

109
00:08:08,155 --> 00:08:10,115
IT DOESN'T MAKE
ANY DIFFERENCE
WHAT I THINK.

110
00:08:10,157 --> 00:08:12,159
BUT YOU DON'T
JUST THROW HIM
TO THE WOLVES.

111
00:08:12,200 --> 00:08:16,204
BONES, I HAVE
A DIPLOMATIC
RESPONSIBILITY.

112
00:08:16,246 --> 00:08:18,748
THIS HAPPENED UNDER
ARGELIAN JURISDICTION.

113
00:08:18,790 --> 00:08:21,626
IF THEY WANT TO
ARREST HIM, TRY HIM,
EVEN CONVICT HIM,

114
00:08:21,668 --> 00:08:23,170
I HAVE TO GO ALONG
WITH IT.

115
00:08:23,211 --> 00:08:26,381
BUT HE'S SUFFERING
FROM A SEVERE
CONCUSSION.

116
00:08:27,882 --> 00:08:29,968
WE'LL DO WHAT WE CAN.

117
00:08:31,886 --> 00:08:33,388
IT'S NOT PROMISING,
CAPTAIN.

118
00:08:33,430 --> 00:08:35,390
MR. SCOTT INSISTS
HE REMEMBERS NOTHING,

119
00:08:35,432 --> 00:08:37,392
BUT MY DETECTOR
READINGS INDICATE

120
00:08:37,434 --> 00:08:38,977
THAT ONLY HIS FINGERPRINTS
ARE ON THE MURDER WEAPON.

121
00:08:39,019 --> 00:08:40,979
YES, MR. HENGIST,
THERE WERE
OTHER PEOPLE

122
00:08:41,021 --> 00:08:43,440
IN THE CAFE
ABOUT THE TIME
OF THE MURDER.

123
00:08:43,482 --> 00:08:46,401
SEVERAL OF THEM LEFT
JUST BEFORE MR. SCOTT
AND THE GIRL DID.

124
00:08:46,443 --> 00:08:48,403
UH, SO I'VE BEEN
INFORMED BY THE STAFF.

125
00:08:48,445 --> 00:08:50,447
THEY'RE BEING LOCATED,
AND WE WILL QUESTION THEM,

126
00:08:50,489 --> 00:08:53,450
BUT, UH, THE OUTLOOK FOR
YOUR FRIEND IS QUITE GRIM.

127
00:08:53,492 --> 00:08:55,494
WHAT IS THE LAW
IN THESE CASES?

128
00:08:55,535 --> 00:08:57,787
Man: THE LAW OF ARGELIUS

129
00:08:57,829 --> 00:08:59,498
IS LOVE.

130
00:09:05,420 --> 00:09:08,006
GENTLEMEN,
OUR PREFECT, JARIS.

131
00:09:08,048 --> 00:09:10,800
SIR, UH, CAPTAIN KIRK
AND DR. McCOY.

132
00:09:10,842 --> 00:09:14,221
AND THIS IS
MY WIFE, SYBO.

133
00:09:14,262 --> 00:09:15,847
AND, UH, THIS MAN
IS SCOTT,

134
00:09:15,889 --> 00:09:17,849
THE ONE I SENT YOU
THE MESSAGE ABOUT.

135
00:09:17,891 --> 00:09:20,060
HMM. HE DOES NOT
LOOK LIKE A MAN

136
00:09:20,101 --> 00:09:22,020
CAPABLE
OF SUCH AN ACT.

137
00:09:22,062 --> 00:09:25,315
STILL,
IT'S BEEN SO LONG.

138
00:09:25,357 --> 00:09:29,403
GENTLEMEN, BEFORE
OUR GREAT AWAKENING
200 YEARS AGO,

139
00:09:29,444 --> 00:09:31,446
WE HAD WAYS OF
LEARNING THE TRUTH

140
00:09:31,488 --> 00:09:32,906
IN SUCH MATTERS.

141
00:09:32,947 --> 00:09:35,616
WE SHALL RETURN
TO THEM.

142
00:09:35,658 --> 00:09:38,412
THE ARGELIAN
EMPATHIC CONTACT?

143
00:09:38,453 --> 00:09:39,829
YOU KNOW OF THIS?

144
00:09:39,871 --> 00:09:41,498
YES, WE'VE HEARD
OF IT.

145
00:09:41,540 --> 00:09:43,375
I ASSUMED IT WAS
A LOST ART.

146
00:09:43,417 --> 00:09:46,336
MY WIFE IS A DESCENDANT

147
00:09:46,378 --> 00:09:48,296
OF THE ANCIENT PRIESTESSES
OF OUR LAND.

148
00:09:48,338 --> 00:09:50,882
SHE HAS
THE ANCESTRAL GIFT.

149
00:09:50,924 --> 00:09:54,135
GENTLEMEN, I HAVE COME
TO INVITE YOU TO MY HOME.

150
00:09:54,177 --> 00:09:56,388
UH, PREFECT, UH, DON'T YOU
THINK THIS SHOULD BE HANDLED

151
00:09:56,430 --> 00:09:58,806
IN AN OFFICIAL MANNER, UH,
THROUGH MY OFFICE?

152
00:09:58,848 --> 00:10:01,476
IT SHALL BE HANDLED
IN AN OFFICIAL MANNER,
MR. HENGIST,

153
00:10:01,518 --> 00:10:03,562
SINCE I AM
THE HIGHEST OFFICIAL.

154
00:10:05,439 --> 00:10:07,399
GENTLEMEN, LET US
PROCEED TO MY HOME,

155
00:10:07,441 --> 00:10:10,651
WHERE, WITH THE AID
OF MY WIFE,

156
00:10:10,693 --> 00:10:12,820
WE SHALL LEARN THE TRUTH.

157
00:10:12,862 --> 00:10:14,906
PLEASE.

158
00:10:24,458 --> 00:10:26,667
DEPENDING ON YOUR WIFE'S
EMPATHIC ABILITIES

159
00:10:26,709 --> 00:10:28,628
IS ALL VERY WELL,
PREFECT,

160
00:10:28,669 --> 00:10:30,671
BUT THERE'S ONLY ONE WAY
WE CAN FIND OUT

161
00:10:30,713 --> 00:10:33,258
WHAT IT IS MR. SCOTT
CANNOT REMEMBER.

162
00:10:33,300 --> 00:10:36,928
SINCE YOU FIND IT
IMPOSSIBLE TO LET US
GO BACK UP TO OUR SHIP,

163
00:10:36,970 --> 00:10:38,972
I CAN BEAM DOWN
A TECHNICIAN

164
00:10:39,013 --> 00:10:40,890
WITH A PSYCHO-TRICORDER.

165
00:10:40,932 --> 00:10:44,269
McCoy: UH, PREFECT,
IT WILL GIVE US
A DETAILED ACCOUNT

166
00:10:44,311 --> 00:10:47,272
OF EVERYTHING THAT'S
HAPPENED TO MR. SCOTT
IN THE LAST 24 HOURS.

167
00:10:47,314 --> 00:10:49,649
Hengist:
OH, I-I'D ADVISE
AGAINST IT, PREFECT.

168
00:10:49,690 --> 00:10:51,859
THIS IS PURELY
AN ARGELIAN MATTER.

169
00:10:51,901 --> 00:10:53,820
Prefect:
MY WIFE MUST MEDITATE

170
00:10:53,861 --> 00:10:56,490
FOR A TIME
BEFORE SHE'S READY.

171
00:10:56,531 --> 00:10:58,575
I SEE NO REASON WHY
WE SHOULD NOT USE

172
00:10:58,617 --> 00:11:00,577
THAT TIME
TO GOOD ADVANTAGE.

173
00:11:00,619 --> 00:11:02,537
VERY WELL, CAPTAIN.

174
00:11:02,579 --> 00:11:04,498
KIRK TO "ENTERPRISE."

175
00:11:08,793 --> 00:11:10,629
"ENTERPRISE."
SPOCK HERE.

176
00:11:10,670 --> 00:11:14,007
MR. SPOCK,
BEAM DOWN A TECHNICIAN WITH
A PSYCHO-TRICORDER, PLEASE.

177
00:11:14,048 --> 00:11:15,342
USE THESE COORDINATES.

178
00:11:18,219 --> 00:11:20,430
ACKNOWLEDGED.
COORDINATES RECEIVED.

179
00:11:20,472 --> 00:11:21,640
KIRK OUT.

180
00:11:21,680 --> 00:11:23,475
McCoy: PREFECT,
THE PSYCHO-TRICORDER

181
00:11:23,517 --> 00:11:25,893
WILL REQUIRE PRIVACY
IN ORDER TO BE EFFECTIVE.

182
00:11:25,935 --> 00:11:28,938
HMM. THERE IS A SMALL
CHAMBER BELOW THIS ROOM.

183
00:11:28,980 --> 00:11:31,566
PERHAPS THAT WILL SUFFICE.

184
00:11:31,608 --> 00:11:34,194
CAPTAIN...

185
00:11:34,235 --> 00:11:36,613
NEWS OF THIS...

186
00:11:36,655 --> 00:11:38,948
FRIGHTFUL MURDER...

187
00:11:38,990 --> 00:11:41,451
IS SPREADING
AMONG MY PEOPLE.

188
00:11:41,493 --> 00:11:43,744
THEY ARE GREATLY DISTURBED.

189
00:11:43,786 --> 00:11:45,372
I HAVE ALREADY
HEARD TALK

190
00:11:45,413 --> 00:11:47,999
OF CLOSING ARGELIUS
TO SPACE VEHICLES.

191
00:11:48,041 --> 00:11:50,960
WELL, THAT WOULD BE
MOST UNFORTUNATE.

192
00:11:51,002 --> 00:11:53,338
ARGELIAN HOSPITALITY
IS WELL-KNOWN,

193
00:11:53,380 --> 00:11:56,424
AS WELL AS ITS
STRATEGIC IMPORTANCE
AS A SPACE PORT.

194
00:11:56,466 --> 00:12:00,470
YES. I BELIEVE
IT'S THE ONLY ONE
IN THE QUADRANT.

195
00:12:02,138 --> 00:12:04,641
CAPTAIN.

196
00:12:04,683 --> 00:12:07,268
Hengist: UH, THERE
ARE OTHER PEOPLE
WE SHOULD QUESTION.

197
00:12:07,310 --> 00:12:09,521
UH, PERHAPS I
SHOULD GO EXPEDITE
THEIR ARRIVAL HERE.

198
00:12:09,563 --> 00:12:11,565
YES, PLEASE DO SO,
MR. HENGIST.

199
00:12:11,606 --> 00:12:13,149
ANYONE WITH ANY CONNECTION
WITH THIS MURDER

200
00:12:13,191 --> 00:12:15,360
SHOULD BE PRESENT
AT THE CEREMONY.

201
00:12:29,583 --> 00:12:32,960
LIEUTENANT KAREN TRACY
REPORTING AS ORDERED,
CAPTAIN.

202
00:12:33,002 --> 00:12:36,839
LIEUTENANT, I WANT
A 24-HOUR REGRESSIVE MEMORY
CHECK MADE ON MR. SCOTT.

203
00:12:36,881 --> 00:12:38,883
Tracy: YES, CAPTAIN.
WHERE SHALL I SET UP?

204
00:12:38,925 --> 00:12:43,012
IF YOU WILL JUST
FOLLOW ME, LIEUTENANT.

205
00:12:44,931 --> 00:12:47,726
SCOTTY,
COOPERATE COMPLETELY

206
00:12:47,766 --> 00:12:49,977
WITH LIEUTENANT TRACY.

207
00:12:50,019 --> 00:12:51,812
MAYBE WE CAN CLEAR
THIS THING UP.

208
00:12:51,854 --> 00:12:53,607
I CERTAINLY
HOPE SO, SIR.

209
00:12:53,648 --> 00:12:55,734
I CAN'T STAND
THIS NOT KNOWING.

210
00:13:04,075 --> 00:13:07,245
CAPTAIN, UNDER
NORMAL CONDITIONS,

211
00:13:07,287 --> 00:13:09,038
SCOTTY WOULD HAVE
NEVER DONE SUCH A THING.

212
00:13:09,080 --> 00:13:11,207
WELL, THAT BLOW
ON THE HEAD--

213
00:13:11,249 --> 00:13:14,085
IT COULD PUT
ALL HIS PREVIOUS
BEHAVIOR PATTERNS

214
00:13:14,127 --> 00:13:15,629
INTO THE JUNK HEAP.

215
00:13:15,670 --> 00:13:17,714
OF COURSE, THERE'S
ANOTHER POSSIBILITY.

216
00:13:17,756 --> 00:13:19,716
EXPLAIN.

217
00:13:19,758 --> 00:13:21,842
HYSTERICAL AMNESIA.

218
00:13:21,884 --> 00:13:24,304
WHEN A MAN FEELS GUILTY
ABOUT SOMETHING,

219
00:13:24,345 --> 00:13:26,306
SOMETHING TOO TERRIBLE
TO REMEMBER,

220
00:13:26,347 --> 00:13:28,849
HE BLOTS IT OUT
