00:25:28,902 --> 00:25:30,946
I'M NOT LYING, CAPTAIN.

468
00:25:30,988 --> 00:25:33,949
I DON'T REMEMBER A THING
ABOUT THE FIRST TWO MURDERS.

469
00:25:33,991 --> 00:25:35,659
COMPUTER, ACCURACY SCAN.

470
00:25:35,701 --> 00:25:38,620
