00:31:38,313 --> 00:31:40,023
A PROPER NAME.

613
00:31:40,065 --> 00:31:40,982
DEFINE.

614
00:31:41,024 --> 00:31:42,818
REDJAC.

615
00:31:42,860 --> 00:31:45,237
SOURCE--
EARTH, 19th CENTURY.

616
00:31:45,278 --> 00:31:48,198
LANGUAGE--ENGLISH.

617
00:31:48,240 --> 00:31:50,492
NICKNAME FORMAT--

618
00:31:50,534 --> 00:31:52,077
MURDERER OF WOMEN.

619
00:31:52,118 --> 00:31:53,953
OTHER EARTH SYNONYMS--

620
00:31:53,995 --> 00:31:55,664
JACK THE RIPPER.

621
00:32:04,590 --> 00:32:06,425
JACK THE RIPPER?

622
00:32:06,466 --> 00:32:09,261
WELL, THAT'S RIDICULOUS.
HE LIVED HUNDREDS
OF YEARS AGO.

623
00:32:09,302 --> 00:32:13,139
A MAN COULDN'T SURVIVE
ALL THESE CENTURIES.

624
00:32:13,181 --> 00:32:16,810
JUST BEFORE
SHE DIED,

625
00:32:16,852 --> 00:32:20,814
MY WIFE SAID...

626
00:32:20,856 --> 00:32:24,443
IT IS A HUNGER

627
00:32:24,484 --> 00:32:27,738
THAT NEVER...DIES.

628
00:32:27,780 --> 00:32:29,615
BUT ALL MEN DIE.

629
00:32:29,656 --> 00:32:31,575
YES, ALL MEN DIE,

630
00:32:31,617 --> 00:32:33,619
AND JACK THE RIPPER
COULDN'T BE ALIVE

631
00:32:33,660 --> 00:32:35,537
IF HE WERE A MAN,

632
00:32:35,579 --> 00:32:37,748
BUT EVERYTHING
WE'VE UNCOVERED POINTS

633
00:32:37,790 --> 00:32:41,460
TO JACK THE RIPPER, WHICH IS
AN IMPOSSIBILITY, ISN'T IT?

634
00:32:41,501 --> 00:32:43,754
OR IS IT?

635
00:32:43,796 --> 00:32:47,173
HUMANS AND HUMANOIDS MAKE UP
ONLY A SMALL PERCENTAGE

636
00:32:47,215 --> 00:32:49,134
OF THE LIFE FORMS
WE KNOW OF.

637
00:32:49,175 --> 00:32:52,345
THERE ARE ENTITIES
POSSESSED OF EXTREMELY
LONG LIFE SPANS,

638
00:32:52,387 --> 00:32:55,181
VIRTUALLY IMMORTAL.

639
00:32:55,223 --> 00:32:58,184
WE KNOW THAT...

640
00:32:58,226 --> 00:33:00,771
SOMEONE OR...

641
00:33:00,813 --> 00:33:03,774
SOMETHING...KILLED
THREE WOMEN.

642
00:33:03,816 --> 00:33:05,984
IF IT'S IMPOSSIBLE
FOR IT TO BE HUMAN,

643
00:33:06,025 --> 00:33:08,027
IT HAS TO BE SOMETHING
ELSE, SOMETHING
DRIVEN TO KILL.

644
00:33:08,069 --> 00:33:10,948
BUT SYBO SAID THAT
IT FEEDS ON DEATH.

645
00:33:10,989 --> 00:33:12,950
IN THE STRICT SCIENTIFIC
SENSE, DOCTOR,

646
00:33:12,991 --> 00:33:16,077
WE ALL FEED ON DEATH,
EVEN VEGETARIANS.

647
00:33:16,119 --> 00:33:19,790
YES, BUT IT SAID
MORE THAN THAT;
NOT JUST DEATH, BUT FEAR.

648
00:33:19,832 --> 00:33:21,374
SAID IT ALSO FEEDS
ON FEAR.

649
00:33:21,416 --> 00:33:23,418
Spock: WHICH WOULD
TEND TO SUPPORT
THE PROPOSITION

650
00:33:23,460 --> 00:33:25,170
THAT THE MURDERER
WAS NOT HUMAN.

651
00:33:25,211 --> 00:33:27,380
DERIVING SUSTENANCE
FROM EMOTION

652
00:33:27,422 --> 00:33:29,591
IS NOT UNKNOWN
IN THE GALAXY,

653
00:33:29,633 --> 00:33:31,802
AND FEAR IS AMONG
THE STRONGEST

654
00:33:31,844 --> 00:33:34,137
AND MOST VIOLENT
OF THE EMOTIONS.

655
00:33:34,179 --> 00:33:36,723
SURELY, PREFECT,
THIS HAS GONE FAR ENOUGH.

656
00:33:36,765 --> 00:33:39,768
SOMEONE--
SOME MAN HAS KILLED
THREE WOMEN.

657
00:33:39,810 --> 00:33:41,687
WE HAVE THE PRIME SUSPECT
IN OUR HANDS.

658
00:33:41,728 --> 00:33:43,981
ARE WE GOING TO LET HIM GO
AND START CHASING GHOSTS?

659
00:33:45,440 --> 00:33:47,359
NO, MR. HENGIST,

660
00:33:47,400 --> 00:33:48,944
NOT GHOSTS.

661
00:33:48,986 --> 00:33:50,696
POSSIBLY NOT HUMAN,
BUT NOT GHOSTS.

662
00:33:50,737 --> 00:33:53,323
MR. SPOCK, CHECK OUT
THE POSSIBILITIES.

663
00:33:53,365 --> 00:33:55,283
COMPUTER, DIGEST
LOG RECORDINGS

664
00:33:55,325 --> 00:33:57,118
FOR PAST FIVE
SOLAR MINUTES.

665
00:33:57,160 --> 00:33:58,370
CORRELATE
HYPOTHESES.

666
00:33:58,411 --> 00:34:00,372
COMPARE WITH
LIFE FORMS REGISTER.

667
00:34:00,413 --> 00:34:02,958
QUESTION--
COULD SUCH AN ENTITY

668
00:34:03,000 --> 00:34:05,002
WITHIN DISCUSSED
LIMITS EXIST

669
00:34:05,043 --> 00:34:06,545
IN THIS GALAXY?

670
00:34:06,586 --> 00:34:09,172
Computer: THE DRELLA
OF ALPHA CARINAE V

671
00:34:09,214 --> 00:34:12,509
DERIVED NOURISHMENT
FROM THE EMOTION OF LOVE.

672
00:34:12,551 --> 00:34:14,636
THERE IS
SUFFICIENT PRECEDENT

673
00:34:14,678 --> 00:34:16,638
FOR EXISTENCE OF CREATURE,

674
00:34:16,680 --> 00:34:18,724
NATURE UNKNOWN,

675
00:34:18,765 --> 00:34:22,352
WHICH COULD EXIST
ON EMOTION OF FEAR.

676
00:34:22,394 --> 00:34:26,690
COMPUTER, EXTRAPOLATE
MOST LIKELY COMPOSITION
OF SUCH ENTITY.

677
00:34:26,732 --> 00:34:28,650
Computer: WORKING.

678
00:34:28,692 --> 00:34:31,277
TO MEET WITH SPECIFIED
REQUIREMENTS,

679
00:34:31,319 --> 00:34:35,156
ENTITY WOULD EXIST WITHOUT
FORM IN CONVENTIONAL SENSE.

680
00:34:35,198 --> 00:34:38,535
MOST PROBABLE--
MASS OF ENERGY

681
00:34:38,577 --> 00:34:42,497
OF HIGHLY COHESIVE
ELECTROMAGNETIC FIELD.

682
00:34:42,539 --> 00:34:44,457
COMPUTER...

683
00:34:44,499 --> 00:34:48,127
COULD
THE DESCRIBED ENTITY

684
00:34:48,169 --> 00:34:51,339
ASSUME PHYSICAL FORM?

685
00:34:51,381 --> 00:34:54,342
Computer:
AFFIRMATIVE. PRECEDENT--

686
00:34:54,384 --> 00:34:58,597
MELLITUS, CLOUD CREATURE
OF ALPHA MAJORIS 1.

687
00:34:58,638 --> 00:35:01,224
FAIRY TALES.
GHOSTS AND GOBLINS.

